WEBVTT

00:00:00.880 --> 00:00:04.800
Kom ons praat oor manie.

00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:07.000
Kom ons begin met Beatlemanie.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:08.750
(Opname van skreeuende gehoor)

00:00:08.750 --> 00:00:11.070
Histeriese tieners,

00:00:11.070 --> 00:00:14.770
huilend, gillend, pandemonium.

00:00:14.770 --> 00:00:16.690
(Opname van skreeuende gehoor)

00:00:17.590 --> 00:00:19.320
Sportmanie:

00:00:19.320 --> 00:00:21.640
oorverdowende skares.

00:00:22.180 --> 00:00:26.600
Alles vir een idee --
kry die bal in die net.

00:00:26.600 --> 00:00:28.000
(Opname) Doel!

00:00:28.270 --> 00:00:30.180
